TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT TGT_Company_SD_EMPLOYEE_SCD_T2.Emp_Key as Emp_Key, TGT_Company_SD_EMPLOYEE_SCD_T2.Address as Address, TGT_Company_SD_EMPLOYEE_SCD_T2.Salary as Salary, TGT_Company_SD_EMPLOYEE_SCD_T2.Superssn as Superssn, TGT_Company_SD_EMPLOYEE_SCD_T2.Dno as Dno, TGT_Company_SD_EMPLOYEE_SCD_T2.Start_Date as Start_Date, TGT_Company_SD_EMPLOYEE_SCD_T2.End_Date as End_Date, TGT_Company_SD_EMPLOYEE_SCD_T2.Current_Flag as Current_Flag, TGT_Company_SD_EMPLOYEE_SCD_T2.SSN as SSN FROM TGT_Company_SD_EMPLOYEE_SCD_T2 WHERE Current_Flag = 1
